//! `metis` command-line entrypoint.
//!
//! Two modes:
//!
//! * **One-shot.** `metis "do thing"` runs a single agent loop and
//!   prints the result. Same shape since v0.1.
//! * **REPL.** `metis` (no positional prompt) drops into an interactive
//!   loop with slash commands, persistent on-disk session, and a
//!   cumulative cost meter. See [`repl`].

